      <title>中国城市进一步放宽购房政策以刺激销售</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-11/chinese-cities-further-ease-homebuying-policies-to-spur-sales</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于销售持续下滑给经济和房地产开发商带来压力，中国地方政府正在加紧放宽房地产市场的规定。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-11/chinese-cities-further-ease-homebuying-policies-to-spur-sales</guid>
