      <title>中国加大人民币支持力度，创历史新高</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-11/china-sticks-to-yuan-support-after-dollar-s-post-cpi-surge</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于美元普遍走强，人民币汇率接近政策禁区，中国表示将继续支持人民币。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-11/china-sticks-to-yuan-support-after-dollar-s-post-cpi-surge</guid>
